Verifications
Configure the layout of sections and fields on the Verifications page. Click the title of a section and drag to the location of choice. Click the gear icon to change section settings. Click and drag the left (dot) icon of each row to order section fields. Click the plus icon to add a tab to the page or a row to the section. Click the X icon to delete a row. Add a section to display information on the Verifications page that is not already there. Please remember to save your work when done.
